****************************************
**      INSTALLATION PROCEDURE        **
****************************************

Tools User
Languages: HTML, PHP, JavaScript, CSS, Ajax
Frameworks: CodeIgniter, AngularJS
Database: MySQL

Requirements:
1. Apache and Mysql server. (Xampp or Wamp)
2. Web browser


Installation:
1. Create a new Mysql database named "solution" in your phpmyadmin.
2. Import the "solution.sql" file into the newly created database.
3. Copy and past the "solution" folder into your htdocs or www directory as the case may be.
4. Point your desired browser to this address "http://localhost/solution"

For the admin portal:
1. Point your desired browser to this address "http://localhost/solution/admin"
